flowchart TD
  ACTION[User action or API request] --> VALIDATE[Schema validation]
  VALIDATE --> AUTHN[Resolve authenticated user]
  AUTHN --> AUTHZ[Tenant, role, branch, and entitlement checks]
  AUTHZ --> MUTATE[Read or mutate domain data]
  MUTATE --> AUDIT[Audit log where sensitive]
  MUTATE --> NOTIFY[Watcher and notification updates]
  MUTATE --> SLA[SLA snapshot or analytics context]
  MUTATE --> REVALIDATE[Revalidate affected routes]
  REVALIDATE --> UI[Updated UI state]
  SLA --> AI[Deterministic AI insight generation]
  AI --> FEEDBACK[AI run and feedback persistence]
